<paragraph id="1C6D4E65A08BB2D752F59199F57B0D2B" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">
<normalizedToken id="F0DAE1174528F1931B7F4A48F70AFE27" originalValue="Gewöhnlicher" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">Gewoehnlicher</normalizedToken>
Flieder
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="8E29F7DF022FD14E554C55571548E80A" pageId="null" pageNumber="12" type="description">
<paragraph id="9C9E95C03C1B543AA74D9076B3BF200F" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">
Strauch oder kleiner Baum, bis 7 m hoch. 
<emphasis id="BE7AAFC70A514A4648FE73EB96E1FE81" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">
<normalizedToken id="036A3A2288FE1AD48F935AA895604F40" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
lang gestielt
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="234EBACBC42C89C5C4D3F8A95646D20B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">
Stiel mindestens 
<normalizedToken id="3CCED6D4A795D6F920B164E68509E6C0" originalValue="¼" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">1/4</normalizedToken>
so lang wie die Spreite
</emphasis>
), 
<emphasis id="376611B793E8C34115E8C2532DE231DB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">
oval bis 
<normalizedToken id="73D1C060D7757A63211DC1BF26037DBC" originalValue="herzförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">herzfoermig</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
, zugespitzt, kahl. 
<normalizedToken id="28FA03B44D881DC2F15FEC7A7C8A5D90" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">Blueten</normalizedToken>
mit den 
<normalizedToken id="A6EB78D4D4DBAFAF1008E624F24C1EF5" originalValue="Blättern" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">Blaettern</normalizedToken>
erscheinend, wohlriechend. Krone 6-12 mm im Durchmesser, 
<emphasis id="BC4F2F6E22EB6B8A253E9A095FC96799" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">
lila, violett oder 
<normalizedToken id="A67F60BDB71B2B2995B996E2C1F07473" originalValue="weiß" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">weiss</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="4747542455E6563C7D7CB1F05F83506C" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="D6BDD882819DFC94FA9968BB1A368078" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="EAE3BB96DB66288C524C5EF287EC9381" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="79FEB32934732AFCB9EFC42DE19EBCB5" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">
<emphasis id="6FB83DD25CB69E6E7496639D2ED31F02" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="88971B77697F2386855A9DD855B9B8D0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">46, 47, 48:</emphasis>
Material aus 
<normalizedToken id="6A551FF343CB64CD6DA4935EE141EF56" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(Sax 1930, Taylor 1945).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5B184C7ECB31C44E4DF554835FD19118" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">
<emphasis id="8CA54EB8BFAE31C5470601C2366CC759" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan. Steinige, lockere, eher feuchte 
<normalizedToken id="AC05BE85F1D20C3C283665D0A565D696" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in 
<normalizedToken id="493DB604EDF29E5F4FA8B8D184FCBE68" originalValue="wärmeren" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">waermeren</normalizedToken>
Lagen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B604A95E746FB8E61F7EEA8CF17AC14B" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">
<emphasis id="2DA4B63F96442AD4931B0794B7A89D2B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">Verbreitung.</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="7375FD183A4C5B744E5A0BA3D3C0C5C4" originalValue="Ursprünglich" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">Urspruenglich</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="988AF8A0250D1651F815B9BDBE254224" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">
<normalizedToken id="448F321A59F0AD89D080E0BE928DE6E8" originalValue="südosteuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">suedosteuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
Balkanhalbinsel (nord- und 
<normalizedToken id="B0F62359D227F3443B23C976576786FE" originalValue="westwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">westwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Banat, Serbien und Mazedonien), Bithynien, Krim. - Im Gebiet sehr 
<normalizedToken id="80DF919C12C42F2B637A697CCCA55D09" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">haeufig</normalizedToken>
als Zierpflanze angepflanzt und selten verwildert (z. B. am Tessin unterhalb des Langensees, im Comersee- und Iseoseegebiet, bei Bergamo).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C3682EA020A721253A8E5C4A32375FA8" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">
<emphasis id="B948D78EAE4D56B5CB04925967DE6B45" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Neben 
<taxonomicName id="69EC5BA824BB94C948771C43A1222C2E" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Oleaceae" genus="Syringa" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="12" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="vulgaris">
<emphasis id="AF704ED855ECDBCA4E227631A9967C19" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">S. vulgaris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sind verschiedene weitere Arten (und Bastarde) 
<normalizedToken id="24290E783C9A983B78253E165EB47655" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">haeufig</normalizedToken>
in 
<normalizedToken id="47A6C9082A3DE64CE1EA4D6D95F9DE48" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
anzutreffen, so 
<taxonomicName id="44560BA129906B121B85C58C1F0D9403" authority="L." authorityName="L." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Oleaceae" genus="Syringa" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="12" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="persica">
<emphasis id="FA35125829092A5AD6FCBBCBF31FBAFF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">S. persica</emphasis>
<authorityName id="5632DAE2B60DEC4DE5E3D8F6EBC5E760" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">L.</authorityName>
</taxonomicName>
mit am Grunde 
<normalizedToken id="8934C328AEC53A4A1EB76DD88CFC1E3A" originalValue="verschmälerten" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">verschmaelerten</normalizedToken>
, lanzettlichen 
<normalizedToken id="64E84FA855DFB6B968D534DB872AB5C3" originalValue="Blättern" pageId="null" pageNumber="12">Blaettern</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
